ZH: 这两个观点同出一辙。
EN: These two viewpoints are totally the same.

ZH: 我们的主意同出一辙，很容易达成一致。
EN: Our ideas are exactly the same, so it's easy to come to an agreement.

ZH: 小明和小李的性格同出一辙，所以他们是好朋友。
EN: Xiaoming and Xili have similar personalities, so they are good friends.

ZH: 这两条路的风景虽然不同，但美丽程度同出一辙。
EN: Although the scenery on these two roads is different, their beauty level is the same.

ZH: 这两种方法的效果同出一辙，都可以达到我们的目的。
EN: The results of these two methods are the same, they both can achieve our goal.

